D2ZwSmw&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=48</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"等等先....<br />\n容易係game搵到樂趣=大部份人覺得好玩嘅定義<br />\n**高挑戰性或者幾高難度都好 都唔代表好玩.**<br />\n<br />\n亞洲market 完全展現到出pubg 係亞洲》fornite 嘅影響性 <br />\n<br />\n各有各玩啦<br />\n邊樣難啲 睇你點玩姐<br />\n細佬我槍game 從來唔玩第三人稱<br />\n所以fornite 對於我來講就算數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046c77403fca049ae7e2c04731f9bb138ab4e7fe","tid":764033,"uid":184932,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:40:14.000Z","msg":"屌你CS  個game 同 fornite 完全唔撚同<br />\n<br />\n梗係難上手啦...on999"},{"pid":"80ad3b46318b9a13d0ce8032c69df0973e759a07","tid":764033,"uid":197794,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"046c77403fca049ae7e2c04731f9bb138ab4e7fe","tid":764033,"uid":184932,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T18:40:14.000Z","msg":"屌你CS  個game 同 fornite 完全唔撚同<br />\n<br />\n梗係難上手啦...on999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T19:02:16.000Z","msg":"咪一9樣，槍法就是皇道。<br />\n<br />\n你玩完高level嘅CS, 過檔去其他game (pubg, h1z1, realms royale) 根本冇難度。<br />\n<br />\nFortnite靜係靠槍法食得屎"},{"pid":"9ee06667520f9b48acaee52b7909a5095fafddc6","tid":764033,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73eca18bd55e319bc7dd055a8dbefd979894a576","tid":764033,"uid":97439,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"集中一個po ok?<br />\nswitch開一個ps4開一個pc開一個大post 又一個 <br />\n你依架又開多一個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T19:55:08.000Z","msg":"其他都話集中姐<br />\n<br />\nPS4點集中<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27edc99b96113958c8f06823894e055edc407dc2","tid":764033,"uid":97439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ee06667520f9b48acaee52b7909a5095fafddc6","tid":764033,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73eca18bd55e319bc7dd055a8dbefd979894a576","tid":764033,"uid":97439,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T15:53: